---

## ðŸ“Š Ranking & Evaluation (APERA Model)

Algo Odyssey uses **APERA (Adaptive Plagiarism-aware Efficiency-based Ranking Algorithm)**.

Each submission is evaluated on:
- Code correctness
- Execution time
- Inferred time & space complexity
- Plagiarism score
- Historical performance
- Timely participation

This ensures **fair, adaptive, and industry-relevant rankings**, discouraging brute-force and copied solutions.

